Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.95,0:03:19.41,Default,Kuroneko,0,0,0,,{Kneel down there.}Qùy xuống nào.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.41,0:03:20.03,Default,Kyousuke,0,0,0,,{Huh?}Hể?
