Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.23,0:12:10.60,Default,Hinata,0,0,0,,{Welcome home, Ruri!}Ruri-nee, mừng chị về nhà!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.60,0:12:11.77,Default,Tamaki,0,0,0,,{Welcome home!}Mừng chị về nhà!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.77,0:12:13.19,Default,Hinata,0,0,0,,{What's for dinner?}Bữa tối hôm nay...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.98,0:12:16.49,Default,Hinata,0,0,0,,{Ruri?}Ruri-nee?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.99,0:12:20.11,Default,Hinata,0,0,0,,{Ruri, are you all right?}Ruri-nee, chị có sao không?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.83,0:12:26.58,Default,Hinata,0,0,0,,{Hey, what about dinner?}Nè, bữa tối tính sao đây?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.46,0:12:31.17,Default,Hinata,0,0,0,,{Oh no, Ruri's broken!}Chết rồi, Ruri-nee lên cơn nữa!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.17,0:12:33.04,Default,Tamaki,0,0,0,,{What's the matter?}Có chuyện gì thế?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.04,0:12:35.09,Default,Hinata,0,0,0,,{Tama, you can't come in here right now!}Tama-chan, em đừng bước vào đây!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.43,0:12:44.18,Default,Kuroneko,0,0,0,,{I'm about to make a very important phone call.}Chị sắp có một cuộc gọi quan trọng.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.18,0:12:45.89,Default,Kuroneko,0,0,0,,{If you two make any noise,}Nếu hai đứa làm phiền chị,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.89,0:12:48.10,Default,Kuroneko,0,0,0,,{the demon king's curse shall rain down upon this house}Lời nguyển của quỷ vương sẽ trút xuống ngôi nhà này
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.10,0:12:51.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{and one of tonight's dishes shall vanish into the darkness.}bữa cơm tối nay sẽ biến mất vào trong bóng tối.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.11,0:12:57.26,Default,Kuroneko,0,0,0,,{Tomorrow, I'll be going to our club meeting.}Ngày mai, em sẽ đến buổi họp CLB.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.26,0:12:58.57,Default,Kyousuke,0,0,0,,{I see.}Được rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.57,0:13:00.32,Default,Kyousuke,0,0,0,,{Then I'll go too.}Vậy anh cũng đi.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.32,0:13:03.20,Default,Kuroneko,0,0,0,,{Okay. See you in the club room, Kyosuke.}Vâng. hẹn gặp anh ở CLB, senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.33,0:13:08.95,Default,Kyousuke,0,0,0,,{I was so nervous.}Hồi hộp quá.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.71,0:13:13.92,Default,Kyousuke,0,0,0,,{I'm her boyfriend now, aren't I?}Mình là bạn trai con bé rồi nhỉ?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.50,0:13:18.76,Default,Kyousuke,0,0,0,,{But what am I supposed to do as her boyfriend?}Nhưng bạn trai thì phải làm gì nhỉ?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.05,0:13:22.89,Default,Kyousuke,0,0,0,,{Maybe I should've asked her if she wanted to}Nếu rủ con bé đến trường cùng mình thì...
